  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patient's sublingual temperature was measured postoperatively on entry to the recovery room.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Adult patients who underwent non-neurological and non-cardiac surgery had their sublingual
      temperature measured postoperatively on entry to the recovery room.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
